<introduction>

<h4>Finding a language learning partner can be challenging, and learning grammar and words through your conversations can be even harder. That's how this language learning platform can help!</h4>
<p>This Simulation showcases the main function of the platform : Partner asks questions in the language that the learner wantst to learn, the learner replies to keep the conversation going. The software detects grammar topics and words use within these dialogues, and offer learner chances to review these topics at the end.</p>

</introduction>
